  <brief_title>Developing Prehabilitation Program in Patients With Operable Pancreatic Cancer Perioperatively and Following Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Developing and Testing the Effects of Patient-centered Prehabilitation Program on Improving Fatigue, Nutritional Status, and Quality of Life in Patients With Operable Pancreatic Cancer Perioperatively and Following Surgery</official_title>
